data.title: Walled Lake Consolidated Schools
data.text:
Walled Lake Central senior Zahraa Khanafer has been selected as member of the State of Michigan’s Department of Education (MDE) Student Advisory Council for the 2024-25 academic year.

Read More about Walled Lake Central’s Zahraa Khanafer selected for Michigan’s Department of Education Student Advisory Council

The Walled Lake Consolidated Schools’ administration appointed Adam Scher as Dublin Elementary’s interim principal for the start of the 2024-25 school year.

Read More about Adam Scher will lead Dublin Elementary to start the school year

The Walled Lake Consolidated Schools’ administration appointed Rebecca Smith as interim assistant principal at Sarah G. Banks Middle School for the 2024-25 academic year.

Read More about Rebecca Smith elevated to interim assistant principal at Sarah G. Banks Middle School
